Por exemplo, se digitarmos o texto “IFSSP” e pressionarmos a tecla </span></span><span xml:lang="PT-BR" class="TextRun SCXW38305865 BCX9" lang="PT-BR"><i><b><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW38305865 BCX9">&lt;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW38305865 BCX9">backspace</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW38305865 BCX9">&gt;</span></b></i></span><span xml:lang="PT-BR" class="TextRun SCXW38305865 BCX9" lang="PT-BR"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW38305865 BCX9"> duas vezes ficaríamos com o texto “IFS”.
